Class Interpreter

  • java.lang.Object
    • corewar.Interpreter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Benchmark, TestInterpreter
    public class Interpreter
extends java.lang.Object
    Object holding the core with it's memory and the interpreter to play each cycle.
